cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DS

This paper deals with the security and management of data in cloud computing, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and databases (cs.DB). It also involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE) concepts. The use of agents for sharing data suggests a possible connection to distributed systems (cs.DS).
